{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 273256, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 52916, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "很大一部分原因是前者没有一个在中国上映吧（据说小蓝鸟拿到了上映许可，可以期待一波）。事实上新海诚的知名度是在君名这个现象级作品在国内上映后才高起来的。", "timestamp": 1598003536, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273260, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 52916, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 声之形上了，不过这个确实差点意思", "timestamp": 1598003574, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273263, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 52916, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "君名确实现象级，此前新海诚知名度很一般吧", "timestamp": 1598003605, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273265, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 52916, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 啊对，忘了这个。但是声之形毕竟是京都的试水作，在剧情上争议多了点", "timestamp": 1598003660, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273266, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 52916, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这有各种原因吧，比如梵高生前那么惨", "timestamp": 1598003668, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273284, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 52916, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "补充下Alice，山田尚子做的多数剧场版还都是有一点观看门槛的（虽然不高），没看过原作那浸入感会差一些。比如如果没看过京吹二季，看小蓝鸟肯定会少很多感情铺垫。另外，山田尚子是京阿尼中生代牌面，说到底还是高级打工仔，和新海诚独立导片子、出成果全都归到他头上还是不一样的。", "timestamp": 1598003899, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273294, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 52916, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不太理解你的名字为什么被炒得那么火。。。个人认为新海诚的巅峰之作是秒速五厘米，言叶之庭、她和她的猫也不错", "timestamp": 1598004036, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273295, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 52916, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "新海诚的叫动画电影，山田尚子叫剧场版，另外声之形真的不如天子君名言叶秒五", "timestamp": 1598004044, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273300, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 52916, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "成功的炒作罢了，我觉得喜欢看新海诚的看过的番都很少", "timestamp": 1598004087, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273304, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 52916, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 巅峰是言叶之庭吧，不过我觉得还是有点尬", "timestamp": 1598004117, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273309, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 52916, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这就是亚文化和出圈的差别", "timestamp": 1598004168, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273776, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 52916, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "个人感觉声之形不错，不过B站那个版本被删减的奇怪（剧情有点不连贯了\n（由于之前没接触过而错过了这俩电影的上映时间\n（不过确实新海诚的电影更容易从二次元圈子走出去", "timestamp": 1598012234, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275144, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 52916, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "大声喊出山田尚子是神！！\n", "timestamp": 1598068299, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 52916, "reply": 13, "tag": null, "text": "凭什么新海诚比山田尚子知名度高那么多？轻音玉爱声之形蓝小鸟不比天子君名言叶秒五强？", "timestamp": 1598003416, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782607, "url": "", "vote": {}}}